column2: SELECT SOA.specObjID, SOA.ra, SOA.dec, SOA.z, SOA.velDisp, PA.petroMag_u, PA.petroMag_g, PA.petroMag_r, PA.petroMag_i, PA.petroMag_z, PA.deVRad_r, PA.fracDeV_r  into GU2#_hw2_w1  From SpecObjAll as SOA, PhotoObjAll as PA, stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust as FSPSG, galSpecExtra as SE, galSpecLine as SL Where   SOA.z < # and SOA.z > # and SOA.specObjID = PA.specObjID and SOA.specObjID = SE.specObjID and SOA.specObjID = SL.specObjID
